properties.areaDesc: Kern County Desert; Fort Tejon; Tehachapi Area
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 26 at 3:57PM PST until January 27 at 12:00AM PST by NWS Hanford CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Visibility one quarter mile or less in dense fog.

* WHERE...Areas primarily to the west of the city of Tehachapi,
as well as south of Lebec along Interstate 5 to the city of
Grapevine.

* WHEN...Until midnight.

* IMPACTS...Hazardous driving conditions due to low visibility.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of
distance ahead of you.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 AM PST MONDAY... ...DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL MIDNIGHT PST TONIGHT
